#Text=Check Internet Data Usage in MTNL
#Text=By providing excellent telephone and broadband services in Bombay and Delhi at affordable price , MTNL has become the choice of many people .
#Text=Many people take internet plans limited to a few GB data usage and hence it becomes necessary for them to regularly keep themselves updated with their data usage details .
#Text=Below are given some easy steps to do so .
#Text=Steps
#Text=Login to MTNL website for this .
#Text=Just type http://register.mtnldelhi.in/jsp/customer/Login.jsp in the address bar of your web browser and press Enter .
#Text=As a web page requesting for username and password comes up have your land line telephone number(through which you are accessing internet ) and Customer Account number with you .
#Text=Customer Account number can be found on your telephone bill under the title C/A no .
#Text=Enter your telephone number as your Username and Customer Account number as your Password .
#Text=Click on Login .
#Text=While entering telephone number as username DON'T enter STD code in the beginning .

#Text=For example : if your telephone number is 27051744 and customer account number is ********** ( it is a unique 10 digit numeric code ) , then your username is:27051744 and password is ********** .
#Text=The site provides you with the option to use Virtual Keyboard as well in case you do n't have a keyboard with you .
#Text=As a new web page opens up find links like : Home , My info , Email Account , Usage information , Customer Care etc.
#Text=Click on Usage Information .
#Text=View your usage limit , unbilled usage , total free and other important details .
#Text=Also you will be shown the duration for which this data is presented .
#Text=You can change this duration to obtain similar statistics for other duration also .
#Text=Now click on Search .
#Text=The result will be displayed in tabular form showing all the details of your upload , download and total data volume .
#Text=Start and end time ( date wise ) is also shown .
#Text=Read , note down or download these details as per your convenience .
#Text=Download button is provided in the bottom .
#Text=After completing your work log out from this website .
#Text=Video
#Text=Tips
#Text=Log out after your work is over to ensure security of your account .
#Text=Enter your Username and Password carefully .
#Text=While entering telephone number as username DON'T enter STD code in the beginning .
#Text=Change the password if you wish to increase your account security .
#Text=Warnings
#Text=Remember
#Text=put " @a " at end of your phone number for eg .
#Text=If your number is 28581515 type it as 28581515@a .
#Text=This is because this is how the MTNL saves our number in their database .
#Text=Your password will be your C. A number .
#Text=Refer to your MTNL bill or call MTNL office to know your CA number .
#Text=If you got error that your Password is wrong
#Text=please do n't give that same password many times because it will cause your number getting locked .
#Text=And it will be pain to unlock it again
#Text=If you do n't understand anything then do n't proceed
#Text=ask MTNL customer care for any help
#Text=Things You 'll Need
#Text=Internet Connection
